<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:55:59 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a597d9ae8a86</link><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;历史悠久的库卡蒙加服务站&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A yellow restored 1930s gas station museum." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a597d9ae8a86.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jul 2026 00:55:59 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a594d327bb67</link><description>&lt;p&gt;女性，黑白照片。女性拥有深色头发，带有细碎的浅金色挑染。她戴着动物条纹太阳镜，身穿石楠灰衬衫。嘴角露出狰狞的表情。太阳镜的反光中可见她手臂的倒影以及部分街道的景象。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Waiting for a bus in NYC to take a friend and I home." height="884" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/era/6a594d327bb67.png" width="884"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://era.some.pics"&gt;@era&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 21:29:26 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a5936f349e1e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;面纱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Forsythe leaves shadows on an umbrella." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a5936f349e1e.jpg" width="1125"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 19:54:30 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a592041235b5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我的绿色自行车的照片，白色轮圈，棕色座椅和车把。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Foto de mi bicicleta color verde con rines blancos y asiento y manubrios cafés." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mijo/6a592041235b5.webp" width="403